@startuml
autonumber
actor "ATCC" as ATCC
participant "RouteController" as Ctrl
participant "CreateRouteUseCase" as UC
participant "RouteRequirements\n(Value Object)" as Req
participant "Route\n(Aggregate Root)" as Route
participant "RouteRepository" as Repo
database "Database" as DB

ATCC -> Ctrl : POST /api/routes (JSON)
activate Ctrl

Ctrl -> UC : execute(request)
activate UC

note right of UC: Validates both airports exist\nvia AirportRepository

UC -> Req ** : new RouteRequirements(minRange, minCapacity, certCode)
activate Req
note right of Req: Domain validation occurs here\n(e.g., minRange > 0, minCapacity > 0)
Req --> UC : requirements (validated object)
deactivate Req

UC -> Route ** : new Route(origin, destination, requirements, distance, flightTime)
activate Route
note right of Route: Domain validation occurs here\n(e.g., origin != destination)\nGenerates RouteID (UUID)\nCreates first RouteVersion
Route --> UC : route (validated object)
deactivate Route

UC -> Repo : save(route)
activate Repo
Repo -> DB : INSERT INTO routes (...)\nINSERT INTO route_versions (...)
activate DB
DB --> Repo : saved record
deactivate DB
Repo --> UC : savedRoute
deactivate Repo

UC --> Ctrl : savedRoute
deactivate UC

Ctrl --> ATCC : 201 Created (JSON Response)
deactivate Ctrl
@enduml,